  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Russian-- not Russians-- Ukrainian and Poland-- Polish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when we come over, that-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] There was a kind of-- of an [? issue ?] in the village, there was a kind of-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Of sort of government, or something of this kind.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was-- he was actually the-- the chief of that one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he tell us, you have to change.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Open-- put away the-- your army-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--dressing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so just-- so I-- I-- what do we have to do?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What you getting at?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he told-- he told us, Jewish will go to the Jewish people, Polish to Pole-- Polish people, Ukrainian to Ukrainian to [? training. ?]",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to-- to here, that he asked me to-- to go to a place, the [? oldest ?] [? mansion. ?] First of all, they didn't want to open the door.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Polish chap who was with me, he was already in civil clothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He told me, I will shoot them, but we have only five-- [LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you couldn't have shot it with-- to the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- but he discharged one-- one of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When he discharged, they opened the door.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I tell him, listen, I-- I have a new German-- Polish dress.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I will give you everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Give me something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He-- He put me in such a scene that you couldn't believe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I come back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had been walking back, in a-- on a side road.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had plenty of tobacco, because-- [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Begging, ?] Cracow, with the-- after the first-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] --day, there was one carriage with-- with tobacco, destroyed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we kept it, whatever we have, to the-- to the-- our [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was in the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
